Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:44.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur4.2\fs68\pos(940,138)}eda ni musubu mi ga jukusu mae ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:49.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur4.2\pos(940,48)}aby neupadla, nežli dozrají.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:49.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur4.2\fs68\pos(940,138)}ochite shimawanu you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:57.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur4.2\pos(940,680)}Bolí mě, když v hojnosti rozkvétám,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:57.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur4.2\fs68\pos(940,770)}kurushii hodo ni mata sakimidareru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:02.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4.2\pos(940,680)\t(3532,4533,\alpha&HFF&)}bez toho však nemám budoucnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:02.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4.2\fs68\pos(940,770)\t(3532,4533,\alpha&HFF&)}asa e tsunagu you
