Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:08.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur4.2\fs68\pos(1600,138)\alpha&HFF&\t(22,814,\alpha&H00&)}nando kurikaeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:14.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur4.2\pos(1600,48)}zas a znovu,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:14.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur4.2\fs68\pos(1600,138)}kurikaeshi umaretemo
